'''''Allium therinanthum''''' or '''summer garlic''' is a [[species]] of [[garlic]] that is found in the [[Mount Hermon]] area in [[Israel]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.haaretz.com/life/nature-environment/.premium-1.585890 |title=Scientists sniff out new species of garlic in Israel |author=Zafrir Rinat |date=April 17, 2014 |website=Haaretz }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://greyduckgarlic.com/New_Garlic_Species_Discovered.html |title=New Garlic Species Discovered |author=Susan Fluegel |date=2014 |website=Grey Duck Garlic }}</ref>

